Package Prog2.src

Class StudentList

  • java.lang.Object
    • Prog2.src.StudentList
  • public class StudentList
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines the properties for the StudentList class, a container class for the Students. The students entered, are stored in a growable array. The methods included are finding, adding, removing, and printing students.
